{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"繼承","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"摘要","title":"摘要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>每個 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\">CSS property definition</a> 都寫道是否這個屬性預設有繼承: (\"Inherited: Yes\") 或是 預設沒有繼承: (\"Inherited: no\"). 這個設定將會在沒有位屬性標註值時發生.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"inherited_properties","title":"繼承屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>When no value for an <strong>inherited property</strong> has been specified on an element, the element gets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">computed value</a> of that property on its parent element. Only the root element of the document gets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">initial value</a> given in the property's summary.</p>\n\n<p>A typical example of an inherited property is the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color\"><code>color</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property. Given the style rules:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>HTML:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This paragraph has <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>emphasized text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> in it.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>the words \"emphasized text\" will appear green, since the <code>em</code> element has inherited the value of the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color\"><code>color</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property from the <code>p</code> element. It does <em>not</em> get the initial value of the property (which is the color that is used for the root element when the page specifies no color).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"non-inherited_properties","title":"非繼承屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>When no value for an <strong>non-inherited property</strong> (sometimes called a <strong>reset property</strong> in Mozilla code) has been specified on an element, the element gets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">initial value</a> of that property (as specified in the property's summary).</p>\n\n<p>A typical example of a non-inherited property is the <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/border\"><code>border</code></a> property. Given the style rules:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code> <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> medium solid <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>HTML:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code>  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This paragraph has <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>emphasized text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> in it.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>the words \"emphasized text\" will not have a border (since the initial value of <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-style\"><code>border-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> is <code>none</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"註","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inherit\"><code>inherit</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 關鍵字允許作者準確地去標註. 這個在繼承和非繼承屬性都是有效的.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\">CSS Reference</a></li>\n <li>CSS Key Concepts:\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Syntax\" title=\"Syntax\">CSS syntax</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/At-rule\" title=\"At-rule\">at-rule</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Comments\" title=\"Comments\">comments</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Specificity\" title=\"Specificity\">specificity</a> and\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\" title=\"inheritance\">inheritance</a>,\n the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model\" title=\"Box model\">box</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Layout_mode\" title=\"CSS layout modes\">layout modes</a> and\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\" title=\"Visual formatting model\">visual formatting models</a>,\n and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Mastering_margin_collapsing\" title=\"Margin collapsing\">margin collapsing</a>,\n or the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\" title=\"initial value\">initial</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\" title=\"computed value\">computed</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/resolved_value\" title=\"resolved value\">resolved</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/specified_value\" title=\"specified value\">specified</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/used_value\" title=\"used value\">used</a>,\n and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/actual_value\" title=\"actual value\">actual</a> values.\n Definitions of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax\" title=\"Value definition syntax\">value syntax</a>,\n <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\" title=\"Shorthand properties\">shorthand properties</a>\n and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Replaced_element\" title=\"Replaced element\">replaced elements</a>.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inherit\"><code>inherit</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"摘要","id":"摘要"},{"text":"繼承屬性","id":"inherited_properties"},{"text":"非繼承屬性","id":"non-inherited_properties"},{"text":"註","id":"notes"},{"text":"參見","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"每個 CSS property definition 都寫道是否這個屬性預設有繼承: (\"Inherited: Yes\") 或是 預設沒有繼承: (\"Inherited: no\"). 這個設定將會在沒有位屬性標註值時發生.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Vererbung","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Inheritance","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Herencia","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Héritage","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"継承","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"상속","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Dziedziczenie","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Herança","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Наследование","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"继承","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/css/inheritance","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/css/inheritance/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance","title":"繼承"}],"pageTitle":"繼承 - CSS | MDN","noIndexing":false}}